    "Id": "chassisdef_ranger_RGR-4X",
    "Name": "Ranger",
    "Details": "Debuting in 3114, the RGR-4X is a comprehensive rework of the Ranger chassis incorporating Clan Endo Steel and Ferro-Fibrous armor alongside a mixed weapons suite. A left-arm Rotary AC/2 fed by two tons of ammunition provides sustained harassing fire, backed by a right-arm Light PPC for additional reach. Two left-torso Clan ER Medium Pulse Lasers and a right-torso ER Small Pulse Laser round out the loadout with accurate close-to-medium energy coverage across all engagement ranges.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Energy</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>",
